No. 105,

Orig.

Kansas v. Colorado.

Motion of the Special Master for interim fees and expenses granted, and the Special Master is awarded $107,199.16 for the period November 2, 1995, through October 18, 1996, to be paid equally by Kansas- and Colorado. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 516 U. S. 1025.]
